1
00:00:01,170 --> 00:00:04,380
(Episode 137)

2
00:00:17,720 --> 00:00:20,390
I'm not Ma Seo Rin.

3
00:00:21,530 --> 00:00:23,030
I am her twin sister,

4
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:24,900
Oh Jang Mi.

5
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:31,470
Thirty years ago,

6
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:35,670
to become the owner of Dream,
that woman, Chae Hwa Young,

7
00:00:36,240 --> 00:00:38,880
stole one of the twins born to
Chairman Ma's son, Ma Dong Seok,

8
00:00:39,340 --> 00:00:41,710
and his lover, Jung Suk Hee.

9
00:00:42,050 --> 00:00:44,720
She stole Ma Seo Rin.

10
00:00:46,750 --> 00:00:48,950
No, she's lying!

11
00:00:50,860 --> 00:00:53,830
Everyone, that's not true.
This is a smear campaign against me.

12
00:00:54,030 --> 00:00:57,260
Seo Rin, what's wrong with you?
You can't do this to your mother.

13
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:59,530
Chae Hwa Young, did you just say
you're her mother?

14
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:02,330
Are you going to keep telling
these disgusting lies to the very end?

15
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:08,370
I'm the one who gave birth to the twins.

16
00:01:08,370 --> 00:01:09,610
Chae Hwa Young...

17
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:13,710
stole my daughter, Seo Rin,
and raised her as her own.

18
00:01:13,780 --> 00:01:15,180
Don't be ridiculous.

19
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,550
Seo Rin is my daughter.

20
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:18,920
Is that so?

21
00:01:21,190 --> 00:01:25,220
She should be grateful
I stole her and not Oh Jang Mi.

22
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:28,290
I'm the one
who lets her live like a princess.

23
00:01:28,690 --> 00:01:31,960
If I had taken Oh Jang Mi instead of her,

24
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:33,570
she'd be the one suffering...

25
00:01:33,570 --> 00:01:35,230
as Jung Suk Hee's daughter
right now, right?

26
00:01:36,230 --> 00:01:38,570
Chae Hwa Young, you heard that, right?

27
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:41,510
Those are your own words.

28
00:01:42,140 --> 00:01:45,910
- Are you still going to deny it?
- That's an AI fabrication.

29
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,850
Do you think I'd fall for that?

30
00:01:48,210 --> 00:01:51,420
Everyone, these people are trying
to ruin me.

31
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:55,290
You all heard the fake recording, right?
You absolutely cannot believe this.

32
00:01:55,350 --> 00:01:57,460
Really? Then look behind you.

33
00:01:57,460 --> 00:01:58,990
Take a look at the DNA test results.

34
00:02:01,260 --> 00:02:04,660
This is proof that Seo Rin
is not Chae Hwa Young's daughter.

35
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:07,370
(Ma Seo Rin and Chae Hwa Young
aren't maternally related.)

36
00:02:07,430 --> 00:02:08,630
That woman, Chae Hwa Young,

37
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:13,740
deceived and manipulated
our family for 30 years.

38
00:02:13,970 --> 00:02:16,640
And when my adoptive father,
Oh Bok Gil, learned the truth,

39
00:02:17,180 --> 00:02:18,340
she killed him.

40
00:02:18,940 --> 00:02:20,110
And as if that wasn't enough,

41
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:22,450
just because Seo Rin was an obstacle
to her ambitions,

42
00:02:22,980 --> 00:02:25,320
she killed Seo Rin, whom she had raised...

43
00:02:25,980 --> 00:02:28,650
for 30 years with her own hands.

44
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:34,290
No. That's all a lie.

45
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:38,460
Oh Jang Mi is accusing me
without any evidence.

46
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:42,000
Oh Jang Mi, do you want to be arrested
for making false accusations?

47
00:02:42,270 --> 00:02:43,330
"Oh Jang Mi?"

48
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:47,040
You insisted she was
your daughter Seo Rin this whole time,

49
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,110
but now you call her Oh Jang Mi?

50
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:49,710
Chae Hwa Young,

51
00:02:49,940 --> 00:02:53,480
you're admitting yourself
that you've been lying.

52
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:57,480
No.

53
00:02:58,320 --> 00:03:01,150
Chae Hwa Young, you got away
with Oh Bok Gil’s murder...

54
00:03:01,490 --> 00:03:03,920
by framing someone else...

55
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:06,360
and even had Noh Cheol Bong
who had confessed in your place...

56
00:03:06,860 --> 00:03:08,530
killed in prison.

57
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:15,870
You're the only one
with a connection to Oh Bok Gil.

58
00:03:16,530 --> 00:03:18,200
You're taking the fall for CEO Chae.

59
00:03:18,570 --> 00:03:21,240
Boss, you can't be serious.

60
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,610
I don't want to go to prison.

61
00:03:23,110 --> 00:03:26,680
If you turn yourself in,
CEO Chae will get out right away,

62
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,980
and I'll continue to have your back.

63
00:03:29,650 --> 00:03:31,550
You'll get out easily too.

64
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:35,650
It's all fake. It's completely fabricated.

65
00:03:35,750 --> 00:03:36,790
That's not true.

66
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:44,160
Chae Hwa Young used me
to cover up Oh Bok Gil's murder.

67
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,830
I have all the proof. I will testify.

68
00:03:47,170 --> 00:03:48,930
Kang Nam Bong, you despicable snake.

69
00:03:49,170 --> 00:03:51,140
Did you come all this way
just to mess with me?

70
00:03:51,370 --> 00:03:54,440
This is neither the time nor place
for a lovers' quarrel.

71
00:03:54,610 --> 00:03:58,640
That's not true, everyone.
This is all a smear campaign against me.

72
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:02,450
Oh Jang Mi is just desperately clawing
for the chairman's position.

73
00:04:02,510 --> 00:04:05,450
You're the one who was desperate
to be the chairman, Chae Hwa Young.

74
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,590
That's why you posed
as the Chairman's daughter,

75
00:04:07,590 --> 00:04:08,990
and because you were afraid
of being exposed,

76
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:11,490
you killed Seo Rin,
the girl you raised for 30 years,

77
00:04:11,490 --> 00:04:13,960
and finally, you even took down
the Chairman, didn't you?

78
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,030
Shut up.

79
00:04:16,460 --> 00:04:18,000
Do you still need more proof?

80
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:22,170
Mom.

81
00:04:22,170 --> 00:04:25,500
I'm shaking, and I'm cold.

82
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:27,440
It's okay.

83
00:04:27,940 --> 00:04:29,640
You won't feel a thing
once the anesthesia kicks in.

84
00:04:30,910 --> 00:04:34,580
You'll wake up prettier than Oh Jang Mi,
so don't you worry.

85
00:04:35,350 --> 00:04:38,820
But why am I so scared?

86
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:46,060
I'm right here.
There's nothing to be scared of.

87
00:04:47,830 --> 00:04:50,700
Mom, I don't think I can do this.

88
00:04:50,700 --> 00:04:52,760
I'd rather do this another time.

89
00:04:53,100 --> 00:04:55,470
Do you know how hard it was to get this?

90
00:04:59,340 --> 00:05:00,340
Seo Rin.

91
00:05:01,810 --> 00:05:04,580
Thank you for being my daughter
all this time.

92
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,880
Now, you can rest in peace.

93
00:05:10,010 --> 00:05:11,120
No.

94
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:16,050
No. That's not me. That's a fake.

95
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:18,760
Turn it off. Stop it right now.

96
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,220
I said stop!

97
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:24,330
That's an AI deepfake.
They're all trying to frame me.

98
00:05:24,430 --> 00:05:27,570
- They're framing me.
- Chae Hwa Young, that's enough.

99
00:05:28,070 --> 00:05:29,400
You're finished.

100
00:05:30,030 --> 00:05:33,370
You raised Seo Rin as your daughter
for 30 years.

101
00:05:33,810 --> 00:05:36,740
How could you murder her so brutally?

102
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:39,710
Even an animal
wouldn't do something like that.

103
00:05:41,150 --> 00:05:42,780
I'm telling you it's not true.
It's all fake.

104
00:05:42,780 --> 00:05:44,280
Why won't any of you believe me?

105
00:05:46,850 --> 00:05:49,950
And when did I ever
make Chairman Ma collapse?

106
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:52,820
It's all fake.

107
00:05:55,890 --> 00:05:57,260
It's starting to take effect.

108
00:05:58,100 --> 00:06:00,700
You murderous witch.

109
00:06:00,970 --> 00:06:03,530
You...

110
00:06:09,610 --> 00:06:10,610
(Stock Transfer Agreement)

111
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,410
(A: Ma Dae Chang, B: Ma Seo Rin)

112
00:06:22,790 --> 00:06:24,020
What is that?

113
00:06:26,090 --> 00:06:30,090
- She's smashing the Chairman's face?
- How could she...

114
00:06:35,930 --> 00:06:37,100
Grandfather.

115
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:46,840
- Chairman...
- He's alive.

116
00:06:46,940 --> 00:06:47,950
Chairman...

117
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:51,620
- The Chairman's alive.
- Is he okay?

118
00:06:59,490 --> 00:07:04,200
You evil creature, worse than an animal.

119
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,630
Father.

120
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,030
How did you get here?

121
00:07:09,330 --> 00:07:12,040
Chae Hwa Young, it's over for you.

122
00:07:12,470 --> 00:07:17,210
Confess to your crimes now
and face the judgment of the law.

123
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:19,180
Chae Hwa Young.

124
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,580
From now on,

125
00:07:22,150 --> 00:07:25,820
you will never see the light of day again.

126
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:30,590
You will rot in prison
for the rest of your life.

127
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:34,890
How dare you make a mockery of Dream...

128
00:07:35,690 --> 00:07:37,960
and harm my family?

129
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:42,130
- Father. That's not true.
- You're lying!

130
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:46,440
You drugged me...

131
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:50,740
and tried to take me down.

132
00:07:50,740 --> 00:07:51,810
You witch.

133
00:07:52,910 --> 00:07:56,250
Take you down? What are you talking about?
If I had, you'd be dead.

134
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:59,180
You came back alive and well,
so what's the problem?

135
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:01,620
So stop slandering me. Just stop.

136
00:08:02,290 --> 00:08:05,390
- You're practically immortal.
- What was that?

137
00:08:05,460 --> 00:08:06,720
You can't blame me.

138
00:08:07,020 --> 00:08:10,360
What riches and glory are you trying
to cling to so tightly?

139
00:08:10,530 --> 00:08:12,530
You should have just given it to me
from the start.

140
00:08:13,330 --> 00:08:14,700
Isn't that right, everyone?

141
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:22,640
This dress is beautiful,
but the restroom is always an issue.

142
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,810
Mom.

143
00:08:28,380 --> 00:08:31,620
- The Chairman's awake.
- Oh, my. Really?

144
00:08:31,950 --> 00:08:33,320
My husband woke up?

145
00:08:33,890 --> 00:08:35,890
What a relief.

146
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:40,290
Then I should ask for my share.

147
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:43,090
It was worth the wait.

148
00:08:43,560 --> 00:08:47,700
Mom, are you serious? What share?
We have to run.

149
00:08:47,770 --> 00:08:50,840
What are you talking about?
My husband's awake. Why would we run?

150
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,440
Oh, my.

151
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,710
Seriously.

152
00:08:55,810 --> 00:08:59,480
Why did you have to be Hwa Young's lackey
and cause all this trouble?

153
00:09:01,110 --> 00:09:05,180
You helped her take down the Chairman.
Now what are we supposed to do?

154
00:09:12,890 --> 00:09:15,560
- What do we do, Mom?
- What are we going to do?

155
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:20,700
Unbelievable.
How could she do something like that...

156
00:09:29,110 --> 00:09:30,140
Chae Hwa Young.

157
00:09:30,140 --> 00:09:32,940
You're under arrest
for murder and solicitation of murder.

158
00:09:33,780 --> 00:09:34,780
Get her.

159
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:45,890
Come any closer and I'll kill you.

160
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:49,390
Hurry, run!

161
00:09:55,230 --> 00:09:56,230
Get her.

162
00:09:56,570 --> 00:09:57,570
Stop.

163
00:09:59,370 --> 00:10:00,640
Or this woman dies.

164
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:05,540
- Mom.
- Mother.

165
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:09,410
- Let my mother go.
- Lee Kang Hyuk, let my mom go right now.

166
00:10:09,610 --> 00:10:13,180
Lee Kang Hyuk, don't make this any worse.
Just stop.

167
00:10:13,450 --> 00:10:15,720
Drop the weapon.
Drop it, Lee Kang Hyuk, you hear me?

168
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:17,490
Don't come any closer.

169
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:35,970
If you hurt my mom in any way,
I'll kill you with my bare hands.

170
00:10:36,270 --> 00:10:37,480
Let my mom go right now.

171
00:10:37,940 --> 00:10:38,940
Kang Hyuk.

172
00:10:39,610 --> 00:10:40,610
Turn yourself in.

173
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:44,350
If you end things like this,
your life will have been such a waste.

174
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:46,550
- Chae Hwa Young is running away...
- Shut up.

175
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:48,550
One more step...

176
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:50,990
and this woman dies.

177
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,520
Drop the weapon, Lee Kang Hyuk,
you hear me?

178
00:10:53,590 --> 00:10:54,590
Stay still.

179
00:11:02,730 --> 00:11:04,170
If you want this woman to live,

180
00:11:04,900 --> 00:11:06,270
have a car waiting outside.

181
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,750
No, Jun Ho.

182
00:11:22,020 --> 00:11:23,020
Mom, are you okay?

183
00:11:24,290 --> 00:11:26,520
Lee Kang Hyuk. You're Jun Ho's dad.

184
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:30,190
How can you hold a weapon
to your own son's throat?

185
00:11:30,660 --> 00:11:33,930
- Let Jun Ho go, right now.
- Hey, you gangster bastard.

186
00:11:34,170 --> 00:11:35,930
You'd threaten your own son with a weapon?

187
00:11:36,270 --> 00:11:37,600
Don't even think about following me.

188
00:11:38,570 --> 00:11:42,740
If you take one step forward,
I'll kill this bastard and then myself.

189
00:11:45,310 --> 00:11:47,610
He's worse than an animal.

190
00:11:48,010 --> 00:11:50,410
- Go get him. What are you doing?
- Jun Ho, no.

191
00:11:51,380 --> 00:11:53,380
Oh no. Jun Ho.

192
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:55,390
- Jun Ho...
- Don't worry, Mom.

193
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:58,060
Oh dear... What do we do?

194
00:12:02,330 --> 00:12:03,330
I'm fine.

195
00:12:03,630 --> 00:12:07,360
- Go, quickly.
- Jun Ho, this has nothing to do with you.

196
00:12:07,570 --> 00:12:09,230
Just pretend
you don't know anything, okay?

197
00:12:21,910 --> 00:12:23,010
We have breaking news.

198
00:12:23,010 --> 00:12:25,250
At a large hotel banquet hall
in downtown Seoul,

199
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:29,150
Dream Hotel CEO Chae Hwa Young
took a hostage and fled...

200
00:12:29,150 --> 00:12:30,550
while police were executing
an arrest warrant...

201
00:12:30,550 --> 00:12:32,420
in an unprecedented incident.

202
00:12:33,990 --> 00:12:36,660
CEO Chae Hwa Young is currently wanted
for murder, solicitation of murder,

203
00:12:36,730 --> 00:12:40,100
and embezzlement charges
of hundreds of millions of dollars.

204
00:12:40,630 --> 00:12:43,770
The police have issued an emergency alert
to all local precincts...

205
00:12:43,930 --> 00:12:46,600
and are securing CCTV and dashcam footage
from around the hotel...

206
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,740
to track their escape route.

207
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:51,310
They are also considering
issuing a nationwide public alert.

208
00:12:53,340 --> 00:12:54,710
(Passport, Chae Hwa Young)

209
00:12:55,710 --> 00:12:56,710
Jang Mi.

210
00:12:57,820 --> 00:12:59,620
What happened to Jun Ho?

211
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:03,050
He got treated for minor injuries
at the hospital and went home.

212
00:13:03,450 --> 00:13:05,960
I think he conspired with Lee Kang Hyuk
to help them escape.

213
00:13:07,190 --> 00:13:08,190
What's this?

214
00:13:09,290 --> 00:13:11,960
Chae Hwa Young was planning
to take a kickback from my father...

215
00:13:12,030 --> 00:13:13,330
and flee the country.

216
00:13:13,330 --> 00:13:15,400
It looks like she was very well-prepared.

217
00:13:15,570 --> 00:13:18,500
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

218
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:21,010
She must have planned to run right away,

219
00:13:21,370 --> 00:13:24,140
but since she even left this cash behind,
she must be penniless.

220
00:13:24,510 --> 00:13:26,110
She probably won't get far.

221
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:30,250
I was determined to catch Chae Hwa Young
and lock her up for good this time.

222
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:32,020
I'm so furious.

223
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:35,050
She won't last long on the run.
It's not easy when she's broke.

224
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:39,660
Today, you went through a lot, Jang Mi.

225
00:13:40,390 --> 00:13:41,390
I'll take you home.

226
00:13:41,490 --> 00:13:44,930
By the way,
your mother must be very upset.

227
00:13:45,930 --> 00:13:46,930
It's too late.

228
00:13:48,170 --> 00:13:49,800
You crossed the line a long time ago.

229
00:13:50,070 --> 00:13:53,340
Come on, Han Young Ja, just give me
one more chance. Look, I'm apologizing.

230
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:54,410
An apology?

231
00:13:54,770 --> 00:13:56,640
You think "sorry" fixes everything
after you tried to have someone killed?

232
00:13:56,870 --> 00:13:59,640
Hey, who died? Did you die?

233
00:13:59,810 --> 00:14:02,350
Gosh, what are you talking about?
That's a bold-faced lie.

234
00:14:02,410 --> 00:14:05,020
You think this is a joke? Get up.

235
00:14:05,020 --> 00:14:08,290
I have absolutely no intention
of forgiving you, so get out of my house.

236
00:14:08,850 --> 00:14:11,420
No, just give me one more chance, please?

237
00:14:11,520 --> 00:14:15,890
I was so wrong. I was crazy.
I must have been out of my mind.

238
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:18,860
I was so blinded by her
I couldn't tell right from wrong,

239
00:14:18,860 --> 00:14:20,630
and I drove a dagger through your heart.

240
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:23,400
I'm so sorry, okay?
Please, just one more chance.

241
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:25,570
The one you should go back to
is Chae Hwa Young.

242
00:14:25,900 --> 00:14:28,240
Go live happily ever after
with Chae Hwa Young.

243
00:14:34,210 --> 00:14:35,280
My legs are asleep.

244
00:14:36,450 --> 00:14:39,020
I'm really...

245
00:14:39,450 --> 00:14:42,320
I don't have a penny.
I have nowhere to sleep.

246
00:14:42,450 --> 00:14:44,720
So, for the kids' sake,

247
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:48,890
don't be so heartless.
Please, just give me one last chance.

248
00:14:49,060 --> 00:14:51,660
If you were thinking of the kids,
would you have done all those things?

249
00:14:51,930 --> 00:14:53,530
Don't even think about staying here.

250
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:56,430
You're a criminal.

251
00:14:56,430 --> 00:14:59,740
If I let you stay, I'd be guilty
of harboring a fugitive. Got it?

252
00:15:00,170 --> 00:15:02,470
- What?
- You should get out of my house...

253
00:15:02,470 --> 00:15:03,970
before the police come to arrest you.

254
00:15:04,210 --> 00:15:05,580
This is driving me crazy.

255
00:15:06,110 --> 00:15:07,180
Chae Hwa Young...

256
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:09,480
I'm screwed.

257
00:15:18,490 --> 00:15:21,730
Father,
aren't you pushing yourself too hard?

258
00:15:22,190 --> 00:15:25,960
No, I'm fine. Now that I've woken up,

259
00:15:26,430 --> 00:15:28,870
my son is here with me.

260
00:15:30,530 --> 00:15:35,470
I'm just so, so grateful that I'm alive.

261
00:15:35,470 --> 00:15:36,610
I'm sorry, Father.

262
00:15:38,140 --> 00:15:41,450
I should have come sooner. I'm too late.

263
00:15:41,850 --> 00:15:43,210
I had no idea that devil Chae Hwa Young...

264
00:15:43,280 --> 00:15:45,420
would completely wreck our family
in the meantime.

265
00:15:45,820 --> 00:15:48,820
If only I hadn't gotten involved with her
in the first place,

266
00:15:49,650 --> 00:15:52,560
- none of this would have happened.
- It's not your fault.

267
00:15:53,190 --> 00:15:58,060
That devil, Chae Hwa Young, chose you
so she could take over Dream.

268
00:15:58,330 --> 00:16:00,960
Whether it was my son or daughter,
it didn't matter who,

269
00:16:01,130 --> 00:16:03,470
they would have become her prey.

270
00:16:03,730 --> 00:16:05,800
We should have caught Chae Hwa Young.

271
00:16:06,370 --> 00:16:08,470
I'm so frustrated and sorry.

272
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:11,280
The fault is all mine.

273
00:16:12,780 --> 00:16:15,580
Chae Hwa Young and Lee Kang Hyuk...

274
00:16:16,010 --> 00:16:19,650
- We need to catch them quickly.
- The police are on their trail,

275
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:21,150
and once the wanted notice is out,

276
00:16:21,990 --> 00:16:23,350
they won't be able to run anywhere.

277
00:16:26,660 --> 00:16:29,530
(Motel)

278
00:16:29,830 --> 00:16:31,260
Former Dream Hotel CEO Chae Hwa Young,

279
00:16:31,330 --> 00:16:33,330
wanted for attempted murder
and criminal solicitation,

280
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:35,700
is now the subject
of a nationwide manhunt.

281
00:16:35,770 --> 00:16:38,140
Police are offering
a 50,000-dollar reward...

282
00:16:38,140 --> 00:16:40,070
for any information from the public.

283
00:16:45,210 --> 00:16:46,340
You need to eat.

284
00:16:47,340 --> 00:16:48,510
There are too many eyes out there,

285
00:16:49,050 --> 00:16:51,520
- so we'll have to make do with this.
- Get it away from me.

286
00:16:52,180 --> 00:16:54,020
Don't you know who I am?
How can I eat this stuff?

287
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:55,190
I'm Chae Hwa Young.

288
00:16:55,290 --> 00:16:56,590
The CEO of Dream Hotel.

289
00:16:56,890 --> 00:17:00,160
Order room service right now.
My personal chef...

290
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:07,330
Ma'am...

291
00:17:13,670 --> 00:17:15,610
Dream Hotel is gone.

292
00:17:16,340 --> 00:17:18,180
You need to face reality
if you want to survive.

293
00:17:27,990 --> 00:17:28,990
Here.

294
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:49,040
Do you know what it took for me
to get where I was?

295
00:17:51,040 --> 00:17:53,410
My money and clothes...

296
00:17:54,980 --> 00:17:55,980
Jun Ho.

297
00:17:58,320 --> 00:17:59,880
I miss my Jun Ho.

298
00:18:00,380 --> 00:18:03,250
Kang Hyuk, please bring Jun Ho to me.

299
00:18:03,620 --> 00:18:04,660
Just hold on a little longer.

300
00:18:05,890 --> 00:18:07,790
I can't even use my credit cards.

301
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:12,300
This is all the cash I have.

302
00:18:13,460 --> 00:18:14,800
We had to escape in such a hurry.

303
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:17,800
I even left the bag of gold bars behind.

304
00:18:18,970 --> 00:18:21,910
- I'm going crazy.
- Just bear with it until today is over.

305
00:18:22,410 --> 00:18:25,610
My subordinate has arranged
for a smuggling ship with a broker.

306
00:18:26,210 --> 00:18:28,650
A boat is leaving for China
at dawn tomorrow.

307
00:18:28,650 --> 00:18:29,680
Until then...

308
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:31,350
hide here.

309
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:33,550
And what happens when we smuggle ourselves
into China? Do you have a plan?

310
00:18:33,780 --> 00:18:35,090
How are we supposed to make a living?

311
00:18:35,550 --> 00:18:39,820
You want me to go back to bowing
and scraping to others?

312
00:18:40,820 --> 00:18:44,860
I can't. I can't live like that.
For 30 years, I've gritted my teeth...

313
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:47,030
and fought to claim my kingdom.

314
00:18:48,070 --> 00:18:49,230
That's how I've lived.

315
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,370
But what is this?

316
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:56,340
I've become a beggar overnight.

317
00:18:57,980 --> 00:19:01,880
Take responsibility for all of this.
It's all your fault, you bastard.

318
00:19:01,950 --> 00:19:04,310
- You bastard.
- Stop it, Hwa Young.

319
00:19:06,450 --> 00:19:08,620
I'm sorry.

320
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:15,760
What do I do?

321
00:19:18,430 --> 00:19:19,430
Incheon?

322
00:19:20,800 --> 00:19:22,400
Yes, it's obvious
they'll try to smuggle out.

323
00:19:23,330 --> 00:19:25,900
Deploy as many men as possible
to that area and catch them.

324
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:27,400
You must catch them.

325
00:19:28,010 --> 00:19:31,580
So that wretched woman is trying
to smuggle her way to China?

326
00:19:31,840 --> 00:19:34,880
Who does she think she is,
trying to escape? Not a chance.

327
00:19:35,010 --> 00:19:38,520
I've mobilized all our security personnel,
and the police are cooperating,

328
00:19:38,620 --> 00:19:40,120
it's only a matter of time
before they're caught.

329
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:42,890
Kang Jun Ho.

330
00:19:43,790 --> 00:19:44,790
Yes?

331
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:47,690
I mean Chae Hwa Young's son, Kang Jun Ho.

332
00:19:48,190 --> 00:19:49,560
Put some men on him too.

333
00:19:49,830 --> 00:19:50,830
I already did.

334
00:19:51,360 --> 00:19:53,060
Jang Mi and Baek Ho are watching him.

335
00:19:53,360 --> 00:19:56,170
(Trustworthy Police, Safe Nation)

336
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:58,100
CEO Chae Hwa Young.

337
00:19:58,500 --> 00:20:00,070
Where is she hiding now?

338
00:20:04,410 --> 00:20:05,410
I don't know.

339
00:20:06,510 --> 00:20:09,410
The last time I saw her was
when she ran from the banquet hall.

340
00:20:11,320 --> 00:20:12,780
Her own son doesn't know...

341
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:15,020
Kang Jun Ho.

342
00:20:15,620 --> 00:20:18,260
You're an accomplice to Chae Hwa Young.

343
00:20:18,790 --> 00:20:20,760
- What did you say?
- You conducted backroom deals...

344
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:21,860
to sell off Dream Hotel.

345
00:20:21,930 --> 00:20:24,090
That makes you a co-conspirator.
That's what I'm saying.

346
00:20:24,760 --> 00:20:25,930
Do you admit it?

347
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:30,430
Detective.

348
00:20:31,070 --> 00:20:33,400
I'm Jun Ho's lawyer,
so please speak with me.

349
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:38,180
Regarding the charges, I will submit
a written statement after reviewing them.

350
00:20:38,610 --> 00:20:42,750
Also, I'll keep Jun Ho with me...

351
00:20:42,810 --> 00:20:44,980
and make sure he doesn't even think
of running away.

352
00:20:45,320 --> 00:20:46,650
So, for my sake,

353
00:20:47,220 --> 00:20:48,720
please don't put him in jail.

354
00:20:49,090 --> 00:20:53,090
- Please.
- Anyway, that's all for today.

355
00:20:53,560 --> 00:20:57,590
However, you're on a no-fly list,
so don't get any funny ideas.

356
00:20:57,760 --> 00:21:00,430
If Chae Hwa Young contacts you,
you must report it immediately.

357
00:21:00,900 --> 00:21:04,600
Otherwise, you could really be charged
with aiding a fugitive. Understood?

358
00:21:08,110 --> 00:21:09,110
Unbelievable.

359
00:21:09,710 --> 00:21:10,740
Seriously.

360
00:21:11,010 --> 00:21:12,740
Oh Jang Mi, Jung Suk Hee,
those darn witches.

361
00:21:13,810 --> 00:21:14,980
I'll never forgive them.

362
00:21:15,580 --> 00:21:18,550
Oh Jang Mi, I'm going to kill you.

363
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:22,290
Looks like they planned carefully
to backstab you on the anniversary.

364
00:21:22,350 --> 00:21:25,520
But how could Ma Dong Seok
become Martin Jang?

365
00:21:26,320 --> 00:21:30,590
I was sure he drowned in the sea
that night. How did he survive?

366
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:32,330
That's what I'm wondering.

367
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:34,970
Anyway, it seems he's very lucky.

368
00:21:34,970 --> 00:21:36,030
What's more,

369
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:40,040
- he became that wealthy.
- Jung Suk Hee screwed me over with Ali.

370
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:42,870
And now Ma Dong Seok
has left me penniless.

371
00:21:43,870 --> 00:21:46,940
How could I let them
get the best of me twice?

372
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:50,850
This is all your fault.

373
00:21:51,350 --> 00:21:54,720
I'm in this mess because
you didn't do your job properly.

374
00:21:56,220 --> 00:21:57,420
Darn...

375
00:21:58,560 --> 00:22:00,560
I'll get money from Jun Ho somehow,

376
00:22:00,560 --> 00:22:01,860
and we'll board
the smuggling ship tomorrow,

377
00:22:02,490 --> 00:22:03,830
so please don't be too upset.

378
00:22:22,780 --> 00:22:24,880
(Blocked Number)

379
00:22:30,090 --> 00:22:32,790
- Hello?
- Jun Ho, it's me.

380
00:22:33,790 --> 00:22:34,790
Manager Lee.

381
00:22:35,490 --> 00:22:36,560
How's Mom?

382
00:22:36,930 --> 00:22:40,000
- Is Mom okay?
- She is in a safe place.

383
00:22:40,630 --> 00:22:41,730
I need a favor.

384
00:22:42,470 --> 00:22:44,770
I'm short on cash for the final payment
on the smuggling ship.

385
00:22:45,270 --> 00:22:48,110
The police have frozen all my accounts,
so I can't withdraw any money.

386
00:22:48,870 --> 00:22:52,340
Can you get me some cash?

387
00:22:53,540 --> 00:22:54,680
I'll get it right away.

388
00:22:55,610 --> 00:22:56,850
Where should I go?

389
00:22:57,250 --> 00:22:58,580
(CEO's Office)

390
00:23:02,150 --> 00:23:04,760
- That must be Manager Lee calling.
- He's going to try to make contact.

391
00:23:05,020 --> 00:23:06,560
I need to ask for police deployment.

392
00:23:15,870 --> 00:23:16,900
What happened?

393
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:19,240
Did you finish giving your statement
to the police?

394
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:20,770
It's none of your business.

395
00:23:20,970 --> 00:23:22,540
Did you really think
I wouldn't know you were acting...

396
00:23:22,910 --> 00:23:25,840
so Chae Hwa Young
and Lee Kang Hyuk could escape?

397
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:30,150
Mom was bawling her eyes out,
thinking you were really taken hostage.

398
00:23:30,480 --> 00:23:31,720
Whether I was acting...

399
00:23:32,580 --> 00:23:35,520
or was really taken hostage
by Lee Kang Hyuk, how would you know?

400
00:23:36,550 --> 00:23:38,390
Then how do you explain this scratch
on my neck?

401
00:23:38,390 --> 00:23:39,590
And why was I at the hospital?

402
00:23:39,820 --> 00:23:41,090
Don't try to fool me.

403
00:23:41,790 --> 00:23:43,960
Then why did Lee Kang Hyuk
just leave you there?

404
00:23:44,630 --> 00:23:47,460
He should have
either kept you as a hostage or hurt you.

405
00:23:47,660 --> 00:23:50,830
- But he just left you behind.
- Then go ahead, report me to the police.

406
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:53,970
Tell them I'm an accomplice
who helped the culprit get away.

407
00:23:54,070 --> 00:23:55,540
Stop talking nonsense.

408
00:23:56,010 --> 00:23:58,610
Where are Chae Hwa Young
and Lee Kang Hyuk right now?

409
00:23:59,110 --> 00:24:00,480
The more you hide them,

410
00:24:01,180 --> 00:24:02,610
the more serious
Chae Hwa Young's crimes become.

411
00:24:03,150 --> 00:24:04,210
And the same goes for you.

412
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:06,020
So, one way or another,

413
00:24:06,620 --> 00:24:07,720
you need to convince her
to turn herself in.

414
00:24:09,590 --> 00:24:11,190
Mind your own business.

415
00:24:12,520 --> 00:24:14,830
If you're so worried, find them yourself.

416
00:24:28,910 --> 00:24:30,740
What's taking Kang Hyuk so long?

417
00:24:31,610 --> 00:24:32,710
This is driving me crazy.

418
00:24:33,410 --> 00:24:36,550
For the great Chae Hwa Young
to be rotting away in a place like this...

419
00:24:38,250 --> 00:24:39,250
What's this?

420
00:24:39,950 --> 00:24:41,080
My hair.

421
00:24:42,420 --> 00:24:44,960
Is all this hair falling out
just from stress?

422
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:46,460
This is ridiculous.

423
00:24:47,060 --> 00:24:48,690
I'm Chae Hwa Young.

424
00:24:48,690 --> 00:24:49,730
My hair...

425
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:53,460
I'm hungry.

426
00:24:54,300 --> 00:24:55,770
I'm starving to death.

427
00:24:56,470 --> 00:24:58,640
Why isn't Kang Hyuk back yet?

428
00:25:01,770 --> 00:25:02,770
No way...

429
00:25:04,770 --> 00:25:06,210
Because I'm broke,

430
00:25:06,810 --> 00:25:09,480
he wouldn't ditch me
and run off by himself, would he?

431
00:25:10,510 --> 00:25:11,510
Lee Kang Hyuk...

432
00:25:12,350 --> 00:25:13,350
Wait a minute.

433
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:16,750
Is he planning to report me to collect...

434
00:25:16,750 --> 00:25:19,120
the 50,000-dollar reward for himself?

435
00:25:19,560 --> 00:25:20,560
That bastard.

436
00:25:21,930 --> 00:25:22,930
Wait.

437
00:26:03,430 --> 00:26:06,040
Jun Ho, don't you move.

438
00:26:06,540 --> 00:26:10,770
I'll risk my life to protect CEO Chae,
so you have to survive.

439
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:12,440
From your father.

440
00:26:49,780 --> 00:26:52,420
Hwa Young, what are you doing here?

441
00:26:56,150 --> 00:26:57,790
You jerk.

442
00:26:58,560 --> 00:27:03,530
Where did you run off to without me?
Did you run off to save your own skin?

443
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:08,600
Why did you leave me behind, you jerk?

444
00:27:09,530 --> 00:27:10,700
Hwa Young, are you okay?

445
00:27:11,070 --> 00:27:12,200
Thank goodness.

446
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:14,640
Are you hurt?

447
00:27:16,810 --> 00:27:18,640
I've been looking all over for you.

448
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:22,810
Kang Hyuk, I'm so sorry.

449
00:27:23,410 --> 00:27:26,450
You know I'm nothing without you, right?

450
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:28,180
I know.

451
00:27:29,050 --> 00:27:30,050
I know.

452
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:54,280
(The First Man)

453
00:27:54,380 --> 00:27:57,710
What Ssangkal left with his girlfriend
is a fake.

454
00:27:58,010 --> 00:28:01,020
So you're saying you have the real wrench?

455
00:28:01,280 --> 00:28:03,620
I handed the wrench over to Baek Ho
as evidence.

456
00:28:03,690 --> 00:28:05,860
Are you crazy?
Do you want to get us all killed?

457
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:08,090
How many more people have to die
for you to be satisfied?

458
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:10,030
Please, just snap out of it.

459
00:28:10,130 --> 00:28:12,800
Chae Hwa Young, for soliciting the murders
of Ma Seo Rin, Kim Bum Seok,

460
00:28:12,860 --> 00:28:16,230
and Noh Cheol Bong,
and for the murder of Oh Bok Gil,

461
00:28:16,300 --> 00:28:17,370
you're under arrest.

462
00:28:18,570 --> 00:28:20,570
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
